Bow Signature Style	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.MarksmanSignatureStyle	VISIBLE:YES	!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE=MarksmanSignatureStyle	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Force-charged Fletching|PREVARGTEQ:MarksmanSignatureStyleTree,1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Lightning Draw|PREVARGTEQ:MarksmanSignatureStyleTree,2	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Burst Arrows|PREVARGTEQ:MarksmanSignatureStyleTree,3	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Rain of Arrows|PREVARGTEQ:MarksmanSignatureStyleTree,4	DESC:Bowyer marksmen are notoriously good at attacking large areas at once, and are most frequently found in military service. A unit of archers led by marksmen could hold off an entire advancing army.

